---
import BaseLayout from "layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Leonardo Alves | Software Engineer"
  description="I am a Software Engineer with solid experience in developing complex and scalable systems using modern technologies such as PHP, Kotlin, TypeScript, Vue.js, ReactJS, and databases like MySQL, PostgreSQL and MongoDB."
>
  <div class="container w-full max-w-2xl p-4">
    <p class="text-md text-slate-600 sm:text-lg dark:text-slate-300">
      I am a <b class="text-teal-600">Software Engineer</b> with solid experience
      in developing complex and scalable systems using modern technologies such as
      <b class="text-teal-600">PHP</b>,
      <b class="text-teal-600">Kotlin</b>,
      <b class="text-teal-600">TypeScript</b>,
      <b class="text-teal-600">Vue.js</b>,
      <b class="text-teal-600">ReactJS</b>, and databases like MySQL, PostgreSQL
      and MongoDB. I have a strong track record of working in agile teams (SCRUM
      and Kanban) and contributing to projects focused on high availability,
      scalability, and technological innovation.
    </p>
  </div>
</BaseLayout>
